# Eval baseline snapshots live here (PLAN-0759 Phase 6 prep).
#
# Snapshot filenames should embed the judge model pin so drifts are
# traceable to model version changes:
#
#   baseline_<yyyymmdd>_<model-id>.json
#
# Example:
#
#   baseline_20260501_claude-sonnet-4-6.json
#
